            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Wrexham County Borough Council invites tenders for the supply, temporary storage and delivery of natural stone materials for our project ‘Town Centre Environmental Improvements — Phase 1’. The works include re-paving part of the town centre.</P>
               <P>The materials will be laid rigidly to BS 7533-7:2010 in a pedestrianised zone but subject to HGV and light delivery vehicle loading on a daily basis. The pedestrianised zone is also subject to winter maintenance.</P>
